145
00:09:50,756 --> 00:09:54,468
Because I know that’s the only
way I could ever comfort you.

146
00:09:55,939 --> 00:09:57,149
Oh, Mom.

147
00:09:57,722 --> 00:09:59,807
You know, when
you were still a baby,

148
00:10:00,182 --> 00:10:01,917
