333
00:20:19,202 --> 00:20:20,078
I’m sorry.

334
00:20:20,078 --> 00:20:22,289
It’s a big decision.

335
00:20:22,664 --> 00:20:24,333
But don’t worry.

336
00:20:24,458 --> 00:20:25,959
I’ll talk to your father.

337
00:20:25,959 --> 00:20:27,377
And I’m sure he’ll
come on board.

338
00:20:27,377 --> 00:20:30,464
