how many times
do I have to tell you?

350
00:21:23,850 --> 00:21:25,686
I don’t love Tony.

351
00:21:26,853 --> 00:21:29,815
I was just scared
to face all of you.

352
00:21:29,815 --> 00:21:31,501
I was scared to face Lin.

353
00:21:32,317 --> 00:21:34,069
But especially you.

354
00:21:35,028 --> 00:21:37,906
Grace, I’m done with your drama.

355
00:21:38,865 --> 00:21:39,968
I don’t want this anymore.

356
00:21:40,575 --> 00:21:43,453
Then why didn’t you tell
your dad that we’re broken up?

357
00:21:45,868 --> 00:21:46,881
Look,

358
00:21:48,458 --> 00:21:51,003
I know that you’re
angry with me.

359
00:21:54,214 --> 00:21:55,924
I can feel it.

360
00:21:57,551 --> 00:22:00,387
But deep down, I know
that you still love me.

361
00:22:09,152 --> 00:22:10,152
Pat,

362
00:22:10,731 --> 00:22:15,195
I just said yes to your dad’s
offer for me to study in Boston

363
