only way that I can be with you.

364
00:22:28,434 --> 00:22:30,895
I still love you, Pat.

365
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:34,333
But I don’t,

366
00:22:37,966 --> 00:22:39,217
I don’t love you, Grace.

367
00:22:39,426 --> 00:22:40,538
I don’t believe you.

368
00:22:41,011 --> 00:22:42,831
Believe what you
wanna believe, Grace.

369
00:22:45,974 --> 00:22:47,309
Yes, I loved you.

370
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,728
But you hurt me.

371
00:22:50,091 --> 00:22:51,642
You lied to my face.

372
00:22:54,232 --> 00:22:55,901
How can I love you after that?

373
00:22:59,905 --> 00:23:01,125
You know what you destroyed?

374
00:23:04,534 --> 00:23:05,540
Trust.

375
00:23:07,579 --> 00:23:08,789
Trust, Grace.

376
00:23:11,458 --> 00:23:14,586
Did you ever really love me?

377
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:19,762
Because me…

378
00:23:22,366 --> 00:23:23,541
Yes, I did.

379
00:23:26,556 --> 00:23:27,778
But you?

380
00:23:28,975 --> 00:23:29,982
Huh?

381
00:23:30,929 --> 00:23:33,015
What, after just one mistake?

382
00:23:33,939 --> 00:23:38,144
One mistake, and it’s so easy for
you to just throw away everything

383
00:23:38,652 --> 00:23:40,529
that we have been through.

384
00:23:50,664 --> 00:23:51,664
Fine,

385
00:23:55,929 --> 00:23:57,212
if you wanna end this right now

386
00:23:57,212 --> 00:23:59,047
then admit to your
dad that we’re over.

387
00:24:03,593 --> 00:24:07,013
It’ll only mean that you
don’t love me anymore.

388
00:24:14,521 --> 00:24:15,647
I’ll understand.

389
00:24:19,693 --> 00:24:23,071
I don’t wanna force myself onto
someone that doesn’t want me.

390
00:24:25,448 --> 00:24:26,491
I don’t.

391
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,516
For this month’s payment.

392
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:53,435
Thank you, Ms. Maya.

393
00:24:53,810 --> 00:24:54,936
Let's talk tomorrow.

394
00:24:54,936 --> 00:24:56,396
There's a new
client that came in.

395
00:24:58,899 --> 00:25:00,096
Ms. Maya,

396
00:25:01,616 --> 00:25:02,616
Yes?

397
00:25:04,237 --> 00:25:08,408
Is it still possible for my salary to
increase if I can get more clients?

398
00:25:09,001 --> 00:25:10,926
I just need to pay for
something at home.

399
