Sounds like a big amount.

401
00:25:18,376 --> 00:25:19,461
100,000?

402
00:25:21,922 --> 00:25:22,797
150

403
00:25:26,426 --> 00:25:27,527
Oh my god!

404
00:25:27,552 --> 00:25:28,762
200,000?

405
00:25:32,557 --> 00:25:33,642
300,000.00

406
00:25:36,311 --> 00:25:37,520
That's huge!

407
00:25:38,271 --> 00:25:40,607
