If regular tutoring, none.

419
00:26:12,347 --> 00:26:13,347
But,

420
00:26:14,849 --> 00:26:16,487
unless

421
00:26:16,810 --> 00:26:19,354
you want to consider
what I have in mind?

422
00:26:20,428 --> 00:26:21,456
I have a client

423
00:26:21,481 --> 00:26:25,902
