Test for International Colleges exam.

424
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:28,655
Stand-in means

425
00:26:28,922 --> 00:26:30,764
the exam is under
the client’s name

426
00:26:30,795 --> 00:26:33,113
but you’re the one who will
go to the STIC center

427
00:26:33,138 --> 00:26:35,599
to answer the exam for them.

428
00:26:36,227 --> 00:26:40,481
That’s one sitting,
250,000 flat.

429
00:26:41,084 --> 00:26:42,961
And maybe the 50,000 shortfall,

430
00:26:42,961 --> 00:26:45,171
