your regular tutoring.

431
00:26:52,298 --> 00:26:54,133
I’m sorry, Ms. Maya.

432
00:26:54,363 --> 00:26:55,371
But,

433
00:26:55,932 --> 00:26:58,893
why did you suggest
this kind of job to me?

434
00:26:58,893 --> 00:27:00,228
Lin,

435
00:27:01,396 --> 00:27:03,440
let’s not pretend here.

436
00:27:03,797 --> 00:27:04,797
I know

437
