background check on you.

439
00:27:11,906 --> 00:27:13,742
Yes, but don’t worry.

440
00:27:14,242 --> 00:27:15,410
I don’t judge.

441
00:27:15,410 --> 00:27:16,453
I don’t care.

442
00:27:16,453 --> 00:27:18,288
That’s why I still
took you in, right?

443
00:27:19,222 --> 00:27:21,683
All I’m saying is, here you are.

444
00:27:22,411 --> 00:27:26,540
Asking for my help to find
you a job for instant money.

445
00:27:27,005 --> 00:27:29,883
