recommendations for other stand-ins.

477
00:29:57,197 --> 00:29:58,197
Grace,

478
00:30:01,576 --> 00:30:02,576
it’s okay.

479
00:30:03,949 --> 00:30:05,325
We’re already here.

480
00:30:06,612 --> 00:30:07,612
It’s okay.

